name: Strawberry Fields 2019
paragraph: The smiles, the sunburn, the sky and the clouds. The strangers, the friends - both newfound and old. That long drive into the unknown, followed by dancing and inevitable laughter. Embarking on adventures through ghost gums, discovering an oriental tea lounge, a jazz quintet improvising on the beach or a disco legend unleashing funk & soul from a treehouse. Long days of wild river swimming and those quiet moments of reflection.
title: A four day adventure in music & art set alongside the banks of the iconic Murray River.

title: Join us for an incredible day out with incredible stallholders at The Hills First Food and Wine Festival this October at Bella Vista Farm!

name: Beer InCider Experience
paragraph: You like beer, cider, live music and ping pong? Beer InCider is the festival for you!
title: We're back baby! Beer InCider returns to Brisbane Showgrounds on 20 & 21 September with all your faves and a heap of new stuff too.

name: Rainbow Serpent Festival 2020
paragraph: For the first time, we will be offering a strictly limited allocation of Payment Plan tickets. Registrations will be open from 10am Tuesday 16th July to midnight on Friday 9th August 2019 AEST or until the allocation is exhausted. Payments will be made via an initial registration fee and three subsequent monthly instalments.
title: Rainbow Serpent Festival 2020 - a multi day camping, music, arts, culture and lifestyle festival

name: The Grass is Greener - Gold Coast
paragraph: The Grass Is Greener
title: The Grass is Greener is all about celebrating good times with friends, listening to the hottest music around under sunny blue skies.

name: Strawberry Fields 2019
paragraph: The smiles, the sunburn, the sky and the clouds. The strangers, the friends - both newfound and old. That long drive into the unknown, followed by dancing and inevitable laughter. Embarking on adventures through ghost gums, discovering an oriental tea lounge, a jazz quintet improvising on the beach or a disco legend unleashing funk & soul from a treehouse. Long days of wild river swimming and those quiet moments of reflection.
title: A four day adventure in music & art set alongside the banks of the iconic Murray River.

name: United Energy Around the Bay 2019
paragraph: United Energy Around the Bay is the best day you'll have on the bike all year! With nine ride options between 20km and the full 300km loop, there's a route for everyone to enjoy.
title: Join Melbourne's biggest bike riding celebration on Sunday 6 October - it's the best day you'll have on the bike all year!

loc: Del Rio Resort, Wisemans Ferry, NSW
name: Return to Rio 2019
paragraph: Every year it gets harder and harder to top our previous antics, but we’re super excited to say – we’ve only gone and done it. Stay tuned, there’ll be more surprises than ever before.
title:
Where all the best people, come together to dream. 
And all of your worries, simply float off downstream.
